<div class="content-page">
  <div class="content-page__inner">
    <h1 class="content-page__title">Changelog</h1>
    <p class="content-page__intro">A record of major updates, new features, and fixes.</p>

    <div class="changelog">

      <div class="changelog__entry">
        <div class="changelog__header">
          <h2 class="changelog__version">v1.0.0</h2>
          <time class="changelog__date">April 2026</time>
        </div>
        <span class="changelog__tag changelog__tag--major">Initial Release</span>
        <ul class="changelog__list">
          <li>150 fully scripted lessons across 7 phases with ~2,400 teaching steps</li>
          <li>Direct Instruction methodology: ~10% new material, ~90% review per lesson</li>
          <li>Natural, varied teacher scripts with multiple phrasing options per step</li>
          <li>68 math concepts from counting to two-digit arithmetic</li>
          <li>25 interactive practice sets covering all 7 phases (341 problems)</li>
          <li>Flashcard system with customizable filters by phase, type, and difficulty</li>
          <li>Interactive visual aids: dot patterns, number lines, tally marks, place value charts</li>
          <li>Teacher/child split-screen lesson view</li>
          <li>Client-side search (Ctrl+K) across all lessons and pages</li>
          <li>Dark mode with toggle in header and lessons</li>
          <li>LocalStorage progress tracking with export/import</li>
          <li>Multiple learner profile support</li>
          <li>Keyboard shortcuts for lesson navigation</li>
          <li>Offline support via service worker with three-tier caching</li>
          <li>PWA install prompt for app-like experience</li>
          <li>Responsive design for mobile, tablet, and desktop</li>
          <li>Landscape mode with side-by-side layout</li>
          <li>RSS feed, XML sitemap, PWA manifest, SEO meta tags</li>
          <li>Open source under MIT license</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="guide-section" style="margin-top:var(--space-2xl)">
      <h2 class="guide-section__title">Reporting Issues</h2>
      <p>Found a bug or have a suggestion? Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/jonajinga/math-direct/issues">GitHub</a> or email <a href="mailto:{{ meta.email }}">{{ meta.email }}</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
